{"tid":602604,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［找數］椰汁咖喱雞配蒜蓉包","createTime":"2018-03-23T06:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T10:03:23.000Z","uid":68594,"like":109,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"2da826cf69023665db1deabd0feb677feb4e8e8d","tid":602604,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:16:44.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係子言張，事隔兩日我又返嚟找數啦，因為聽日會去幾日旅行嘅關係，所以就係時候清下個雪櫃啲食材，上次剩低嗰啲甘筍、洋蔥同薯仔，今晚屋企又有啲雞翼未食晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁啱又記得有人問有啲乜嘢家常小菜比較方便，所以就落街買樽咖喱醬整個椰汁咖喱雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係,我係用咖喱醬嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/140403_122fc1a2d9e117f001952ed17d153c9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F140403_122fc1a2d9e117f001952ed17d153c9d.png&h=7768e412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料有<br />\n雞翼/雞髀：四五隻<br />\n洋蔥：一隻<br />\n薯仔：三個<br />\n甘筍：半條<br />\n薑、蔥、蒜頭：幾粒<br />\n椰漿：一罐細<br />\n<br />\n仲有一條法國麵包係攞嚟整蒜蓉包用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/140915_0d290a267cc0a5e2ae12c12c4c20b055.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F140915_0d290a267cc0a5e2ae12c12c4c20b055.png&h=d0782136&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/140918_efeeae94dc993a7022749d3ee2d641a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F140918_efeeae94dc993a7022749d3ee2d641a1.png&h=c0bd3b85&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/140920_96ba700d52ff7d1995348368934e20b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F140920_96ba700d52ff7d1995348368934e20b2.png&h=4c07238d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先我哋梗係要醃咗啲雞先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用啲生抽、鹽、糖、米酒醃佢半個鐘就OK，之後就落油，煎香左有皮嗰邊先，然後反轉煎多一兩分鐘，跟住就可以拎起放埋一邊備用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141111_33bb98ff442bb52dd9494700137e13ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141111_33bb98ff442bb52dd9494700137e13ec.png&h=c7d98bff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141114_fb5d289c7fb1471050e274da1ddafc26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141114_fb5d289c7fb1471050e274da1ddafc26.png&h=f5d97348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洋蔥甘筍薯仔求其切幾下，乾蔥、蒜頭同薑就要切都好碎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141229_ebcc5e290ed54256656ff8295d7ebd85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141229_ebcc5e290ed54256656ff8295d7ebd85.png&h=082b0e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141230_338aa243744e5ae05e46f067dc0008bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141230_338aa243744e5ae05e46f067dc0008bc.png&h=6d79ff1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141231_7cce5bde7116f927abf19fa977f10e46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141231_7cce5bde7116f927abf19fa977f10e46.png&h=6c2bda29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141233_658e7cef0d66d289f3932c690b8c6b11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141233_658e7cef0d66d289f3932c690b8c6b11.png&h=017b024b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用剩低嘅雞油起鑊，爆香左啲乾蔥蒜頭同薑先，然後就攞埋啲洋蔥一整炒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141355_f412b39be874b15c63ab07aa0b5417f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141355_f412b39be874b15c63ab07aa0b5417f7.png&h=de97dec4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141356_737c2f2aae16829e855eb2211c084744.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141356_737c2f2aae16829e855eb2211c084744.png&h=2ae63b02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141358_8b19f97208b1c581db27f69374592e4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141358_8b19f97208b1c581db27f69374592e4d.png&h=28437374&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141359_3ca8a5b5c1b27f4c772a6b54758e681e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141359_3ca8a5b5c1b27f4c772a6b54758e681e.png&h=892f2c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n炒到咁上下就可以落咖喱醬，大約一匙羹左右，跟住就可以落埋啲薯仔同埋甘筍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141501_7f7013e01e6f7f50e9c42323628bd6cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141501_7f7013e01e6f7f50e9c42323628bd6cb.png&h=72ca2f59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141503_029020bfd65010a8523d4326c42189ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141503_029020bfd65010a8523d4326c42189ee.png&h=ff374225&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141505_bb5c22cacc4a057df485252eec7a0a74.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141505_bb5c22cacc4a057df485252eec7a0a74.png&h=174a60d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就可以落埋啲雞肉同埋水，啲水夠啱啱好蓋過啲雞就OK，之後攞埋罐椰漿，有佢煮返30分鐘-45分鐘就OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db0ecfabad811470ef48b59bdfc5fb8feaa5fb0","tid":602604,"uid":68594,"like":142,"dislike":6,"score":136,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"係煮緊咖喱雞嘅時候，咁我哋就要爭取時間整埋蒜蓉包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141721_d6368f7102b5dcf5b4965347c2878d63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141721_d6368f7102b5dcf5b4965347c2878d63.png&h=b4250864&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141723_5246cbb21efa53b15e83404b61a7d5bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141723_5246cbb21efa53b15e83404b61a7d5bf.png&h=c914950c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n切碎啲蒜頭，加啲鹽同埋香草，之後同牛油混合，牛油要預先攞返係室溫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141823_beeef587d3f5b683597d08d71c05d9dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141823_beeef587d3f5b683597d08d71c05d9dd.png&h=56836416&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141825_b5f98b435084a25eae0d262aad11dc04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141825_b5f98b435084a25eae0d262aad11dc04.png&h=d4ae55a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141826_e80f20a265c8293d8f893166930f40c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141826_e80f20a265c8293d8f893166930f40c0.png&h=b0b88c60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麵包切片，搽牛油，之後入焗爐180度淨係要上火，焗大約7至8分鐘就可以啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141923_c4b756f9ec672d585d6c5fc018adac46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141923_c4b756f9ec672d585d6c5fc018adac46.png&h=34f143a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/141943_b7729ecafea3a1ee090f633b31d1f164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F141943_b7729ecafea3a1ee090f633b31d1f164.png&h=7b155573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與此同時咖喱雞應該都差唔多煮好，咁就可以上碟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/142017_436a8acc5f82f8e74e7a7594ff8ac332.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F142017_436a8acc5f82f8e74e7a7594ff8ac332.png&h=7d7f3e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/142018_86bed97d073be215715fb20a12de6e8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F142018_86bed97d073be215715fb20a12de6e8d.png&h=05487469&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/142020_86bed97d073be215715fb20a12de6e8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F142020_86bed97d073be215715fb20a12de6e8d.png&h=100b6316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後今日冇乜補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以都係果句，下次繼續找數！bye！"},{"pid":"665a7b12aaca06fc9cc30a7ca10f4858cfbda598","tid":602604,"uid":1707,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:30:45.000Z","msg"